 The lvl 30 spell would kill mobs lvl 15 or less. I honestly don’t think this is to unpractical because it would give us something to defend ourselves in dungeons like the warrens where you have 14 lvl 7's all attacking you and you Keep on getting Interuped and it would give us something to make our class somewhat desirable in some situations.  Its just my stupid idea, if you have another ideas id like to hear them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uglinlor00.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glinlor00</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Site Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><br><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif><a href=mailto:glinlor@graffe.com style=text-decoration: none><font color=#FFFFFF>Contact Glinlor</font></a></font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 998<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/7/02 11:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: idea for some green mobs</span><hr size=1> I'm going to move this to the correct forum for this topic-Mod.<br>
